item.title: How To Travel To Indonesia In 2022
item.description: Traveling is one of the most important ways to fulfill our curiosity as human beings, but since the pandemic started, traveling, especially international travels, came to a halt because of all the safety measures. It’s the beginning of 2022 now, while traveling is not as strict as when the pandemic just started, its definitely not as easy to travel as pre pandemic times.
